story_teamgalactic_01_08000/2401_1201_01: Sorry, but do you mind if we split up here?
story_teamgalactic_01_08000/2401_1201_02:
I think it’ll be more efficient to scope out the
enemy separately than as a group.
story_teamgalactic_01_08000/2401_1201_04: OK! I trust your judgment, Cynthia!
story_teamgalactic_01_08000/2401_1201_08: So, what’s our plan for getting into the hideout?
story_teamgalactic_01_08000/2401_1201_09:
Well, obviously we just gotta barge in through the
front door, right?
story_teamgalactic_01_08000/2401_1201_10:
Yeah. If we draw all the attention to us, I bet that
would make things easier on Cynthia, too.
story_teamgalactic_01_08000/2401_1201_12: Haha! I’m glad you’re on board!
story_teamgalactic_01_08000/2401_1201_13: Let’s do this! Ready or not, here we come!
